latestIgtvVideos.title: Tribute To Sushant Singh Rajput
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I really can't believe this. Its actually so heartbreaking. This is my favourite song . I watch Qaafiraana's music video every day just for the "chai" scene. It hit me so hard while i was editing this video that the person in my dream scene is no more. Rest In Peace Sushant Singh Rajput, I'm sorry that your world failed you. 
PLEASE Check up on people who are close to you, The times are extremely confusing and tough, Call your friends and loved ones, Tell them that you love them. 
And if you're someone who is going through a bad phase Talk to someone, ask for a hug, take some time out for yourself, YOU ARE NOT ALONE ❤️
Mental health is not a joke and Depression is not a choice. Please Be there for each other❤️
.
.
.
.
.
.
